      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GATE TWO SLOY (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Unplug Ben (26.74) in a Mix. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Sure to be about the mark. MIDNIGHT HOYEON (7) charged out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but swamped late when a close up fourth (30.13) at Richmond over 520m. One of the main contenders. KING ZEAL (6) rocketed around 365m at Nowra in 20.33 three back then has been in the money the last two since. Must include on winning run three back. SPENCER BANNER (5) gave nothing else a chance most recently. Hard to beat again.",
